{
  "texts": [
    "Correctly answering these questions requires detailed analysis of the given information and multi-step logical reasoning, calculating chords, melodies, scales, rhythms, etc.",
    "We initialized a fp16-precision ChatMusician-Base from the LLaMA2-7B-Base weights (Touvron et al., 2023a,b), and applied a continual pre-training plus fine-tuning pipeline.",
    "The data settings will be introduced later.",
    "LoRA adapters (Hu et al., 2021) were integrated into the attention and MLP layers, with additional training on embeddings and all linear layers.",
    "The maximum sequence length was 2048."
  ]
}